headline: Conagra Brands Named to Military Times' 2024 Best for Vets: Employers List
summary: Conagra Brands, Inc. (NYSE: CAG) today announced that it has been recognized on the 2024 Best for Vets: Employers list by Military Times. This recognition comes as the company continues to demonstrate its dedication to supporting veterans and active-duty service members, as well as their families, through strategic partnerships and internal initiatives.
